Market Segmentation: 
The knee pads market is segmented on the basis of type, material type, price, consumer group, application and end use. The growth amongst these segments will help you analyze meagre growth segments in the industries, and provide the users with valuable market overview and market insights to help them in making strategic decisions for identification of core market applications.
Knee pads market on the basis of type has been segmented into basic, industrial, military and sports.
Based on material type, the knee pads market has been segmented into foam, gel, nylon, polyvinyl chloride (PVC) and rubber.
Based on price, the knee pads market has been segmented into under $25, $25-$50, $51-$100, and above $100.
On the basis of consumer group, the knee pads market has been segmented into kids, women and men. Women have been sub-segmented into teenagers, adults and senior citizens. Men have also been sub-segmented as teenagers, adults and senior citizens.
On the basis of application, the knee pads market has been segmented into industrial, tactical and safety.
Knee pads market has also been segmented into individual and industrial on the basis of end use.
